---
title: Honey & Garlic Chicken Strips with Creamy Potato Salad & Veggies
description: Not to toot our own horn, but we certainly know how to capture the beautiful flavours of classic combos like garlic
and honey. We’ve used these two simple things for inspiration by coating succulent chicken in a tasty seasoning, then teaming it with a creamy dill-parsley potato salad for a delicious and nutritionally balanced meal. Thank us for it later!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

*Keep an eye out...Due to recent sourcing challenges, we’ve replaced baby broccoli with broccoli, and baby spinach which may be a little different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
